#5: src/prj_kernel_api/tool_gateway.py marked deprecated (DeprecationWarning on import)
#7: telemetry.py: 3 new context metrics (compile, extraction, promote)
    context_compiler.py: compile telemetry hook wired
#9: canonical_store query: _is_fresh + _needs_review metadata on each result

367 tests passing, all lint clean.

